OL,5,G1650 Four in a Bed
OL,6,     FThe B&Bers head off to the great
OL,7,     Foutdoors at Eden Valley Glamping
OL,8,     Fsite in Armathwaite, Cumbria,
OL,9,     Fwhere hosts Liz and Dave hope to
OL,10,     Fconvert their guests with their
OL,11,     Fback-to-basics approach.
OL,12,G1720 Four in a Bed
OL,13,     FNeil and Mary Blackburn welcome
OL,14,     Ftheir rivals to Fernie Castle in
OL,15,     FFife. There's plenty of
OL,16,     Ftraditional Scots splendour on
OL,17,     Fshow, but two guests aren't
OL,18,     Fimpressed by the continental
OL,19,     Fbreakfast.
